| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3672 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 45d30c02-3286-583d-9caa-5d838c6c4ad0"
